casebody.data:
Miscellaneous Orders.

No. 275. No. 276. No. 119, Misc. No. 120, Misc. Kilpatrick v. Texas & Pacific Railway Co.; Parker v. Texas & Pacific Railway Co.; Ex parte Kilpatrick; and Ex parte Parker. William H. DeParcq for petitioners. John M. Scott and William H. Timbers for respondent.

In Nos. 275 and 276 the petition for writs of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit- is denied. In Nos. 119, Misc. and 120, Misc., the motion for leave to file petition for writs of prohibition is denied.
